<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>سُورَةُ الرَّحْمَن<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>تَفْسِيرُ السُّورَة<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c3">{الشَّمْسُ وَالْقَمَرُ بِحُسْبَانٍ}</span> <span class="c2">(١)</span><a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c5">قَالَ الْبُخَارِيُّ ج٤ص١٠٧:</span> قَالَ مُجَاهِدٌ: كَحُسْبَانِ الرَّحَى.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c5">وَقَالَ غَيْرُهُ:</span> بِحِسَابٍ وَمَنَازِلَ , لَا يَعْدُوَانِهَا.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c5">حُسْبَانٌ:</span> جَمَاعَةُ حِسَابٍ، مِثْلُ شِهَابٍ , وَشُهْبَانٍ.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<hr>
<p class="hamesh">(١) [الرحمن: ٥]</p> </div>